metadata.name: Savoury Blaze
metadata.description:
A struggle to harness the energy you’ve kept for a long time owing to unsettled feelings, occupied negativity, reluctancy and questioning yourself whether you are a self taught procrastinators or just plain lazy. You convinced that you are capable and will do wonders but there’s always a ‘but’ on the bridge of a sentence. It’s an experience you feel when you’re on a situation where reality comes to check up on you and rains you with question of living. It have to be a beautiful ending if we believe that we are the author of our own narration. Everything has its phase and everything will evolve.
